  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Techniques: Blue </p><p>Prerequisite: Transforming Apparatus </p><p></p><p>While inert, your puppet looks like a normal mechanical object of a size equal to its original form.</p><p> Your puppet can transform into a box, briefcase, or other similar objects.</p><p> You and your puppet gain proficiency in Deception and Stealth skills; if you already have proficiency in these skills, you instead gain Mastery.</p><p> You can make your puppet transform as an object interaction as long as you can touch it.</p><p> If you hide your puppet from an enemy they are surprised.</p><p></p>",
